data.description: Fantastic Elmwood Park ranch style home in the perfect location.   Your right in between Conti Parkway ("The Circle"= Civic center, restaurants, water park, recreation area) and Elmwood Parks very own Resturaunt row.  This property features three large bedrooms, two full bathrooms, recently refinished flooring and brand new ceramic tile in the basement.  Lastly this property has also passed the Elmwood Park Village inspection and is ready to be yours today.
